Delphine Arnault - Wikipedia





















 






Delphine Arnault

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Delphine Arnault


Born
Delphine Arnault
(1975-04-04) 4 April 1975 (age 42)
Neuilly-sur-Seine, France


