Biography[edit]
Education and early career[edit]
Delphine Arnault received her degree from the London School of Economics and EDHEC Business School (Ecole des Hautes Etudes Commerciales du Nord), she began her career working for the strategy consulting firm McKinsey and Company. She joined LMVH in 2000.[1]
LVMH (Moet Hennessy Louis Vuitton)[edit]
